 our Rastall-like model to standard (astrophysical\nand cosmological) gravitational scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Sep 2022 17:31:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 12:57:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-20"}
