gests that the dust is distributed in an\nextended flat disk, and finds a mean inclination angle of 49$^{+3}_{-13}$\ndegrees.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 3 Sep 2022 12:10:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
